highlights.text: Omer Adam has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “ראיתי עולם” is the highest at #7.
“Bye Bye Bye - From Deadpool and Wolverine Soundtrack” by *NSYNC is the highest new entry on Top Songs Israel at #76.
“חרבו דרבו” by STILLA and Ness is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 106 spots at #55.
“לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 334 weeks straight.
